AstroPaper — License

This repository contains two kinds of material with different licenses:

1. Workflow, scripts, and agent-facing instructions — the shell
   scripts, repository structure, report templates, the public research-
   profile template, and the prompting/instruction material in README.md
   and doc/template_research_profile.md — are licensed under the MIT
   License (below). The MIT text refers to "Software" throughout; here
   that term is applied, equivalently, to this prompt-driven workflow
   material.

2. Dated reports and prose — the reports under YYYY/ folders
   (e.g. 2026/arXiv_*.md) are individual editorial works and are
   licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
   License (CC BY 4.0). Full text:
   https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

If you reuse this workflow for another project, you may apply the MIT
License to your fork of the scaffolding. If you cite, quote, or
redistribute one of the reports, attribute the original author and link
back to this repository.

